                        <note rend="inline" type="source">817.041/16: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to the Chargé in Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Munro</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-09-28T18:00:00-05:00"><hi rend="italic">September 28,
                                        1927—6 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>149. Your 254, September 27, 10 a.m. Solution outlined by you is
                            satisfactory to the Department.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Carr</hi></signed></closer>
